The police&#8217;s Moatshe Ngoepe says the men are heavily armed and considered to be dangerous. JOHANNESBURG Limpopo police are still searching for 18 suspects who made off with an undisclosed amount of money stolen from an ATM in Burgersfort.It's alleged that the suspects stormed into a local bank at a complex in the area instructed security officials to lie down before opening fire, killing one guard instantly.The police s Moatshe Ngoepe says the men are heavily armed and considered to be dangerous. He's urged anyone with information to come forward. We re still following the suspects and we appeal to all members of the community who might be aware of their identification to call us or the nearest police station on our Crime Line Stop 08600 10111. 